      "review_summary": "The PR adds `gateway.tools.byNode`, threads an authenticated `hostingNodeId` through node-originated agent runs, filters embedded tools by that node policy, and adds docs plus focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +136, Tests +150, Docs +19. Total +305 across 15 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review finding: source inspection shows the PR adds new `FIELD_HELP` keys without matching `FIELD_LABELS`, and the existing config help quality test enforces that parity. Not applicable as a bug reproduction for the byNode feature itself; the PR supplies paired-node live output for the intended behavior.",
